These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, mirinda, tea
4 different pets are kept: fish, dog, goat, horse
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person drinking cola and the owner of the dog##2
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere between the person drinking tea and the person drinking cola##7
4. the owner of the dog is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking tea is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
6. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the fish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | mirinda | tea       | hot-chocolate | cola        |
| Pet      | goat  | dog | horse        | fish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, hedgehog, snake
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, lilac, yellow, chestnut
1. the person who likes chestnut is somewhere between the person who likes yellow and the owner of the hedgehog##7
2. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the left of the owner of the dog##5
3. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the right of the person who likes chestnut##5
4. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
5. the person who likes chestnut is between the person who likes yellow and the person who likes lilac##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Pet     | hedgehog | goat       | snake         | dog     |
| Color   | lilac   | chestnut | yellow | fuchsia |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, crime, mystery, scientific
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, siglo, bluemaster, swisher
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
2. the swisher-smoker is somewhere between the siglo-smoker and the bolivar-smoker##7
3. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the bolivar-smoker is somewhere between the swisher-smoker and the person watching crime movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | scientific | mystery | comedy  |
| Cigar   | bluemaster | bolivar  | swisher   | siglo |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, traveling, woodworking, writing
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, aquamarine, yellow, brown
1. the person who likes brown is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere between the person who likes aquamarine and the person who's hobby is writing##7
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person who likes brown##1
4. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Hobby   | traveling | collecting | writing       | woodworking |
| Color   | aquamarine      | turquise   | yellow | brown  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, reading, rock-climbing, video-games
There 4 different types of food: grapes, asparagus, radish, apple
1. the person eating apple is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
2. the person eating grapes is somewhere to the left of the person eating asparagus##5
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
4. the person eating apple is somewhere between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is drawing##7
5. the person eating apple is on the left of the person eating radish##1
6. the person eating asparagus is somewhere to the left of the person eating apple##5
7. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | drawing   | video-games | reading |
| Food   | grapes      | asparagus | apple      | radish |

