.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, mirinda, sprite
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, black, aquamarine, orange
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
2. the person who likes aquamarine is the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person who likes black is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person who likes orange##3
6. the person who likes orange is somewhere between the person who likes turquise and the person who likes black##7
7. the person who likes aquamarine is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | 7up      | mirinda | sprite     |
| Color   | turquise    | orange | black   | aquamarine |

