.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-7::.
There 4 different types of food: cherry, grapefruit, orange, pepper
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, time-travel, animation, mystery
1. the person watching musical movies is on the far left##1
2. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
3. the person eating pepper is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere between the person eating cherry and the person eating orange##7
5. the person watching animation movies is somewhere to the left of the person eating orange##5
6. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food          | pepper    | cherry   | grapefruit | orange  |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | animation | mystery    | time-travel |

