.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, argentine, colombian, spanish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, volleyball, sailing, soccer
1. the argentine is not the person who's sport is soccer##6
2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
3. the spanish is the person who's sport is sailing##1
4. the colombian is somewhere between the spanish and the american##7
5. the argentine is on the left of the american##1
6. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
7. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | spanish | colombian | argentine | american |
| Sport           | sailing   | soccer    | skiing       | volleyball  |

