.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-10::.
City: edinburgh, paris, prague, boston
4 different pets are kept: dog, mouse, rat, snake
1. the person traveling to boston is somewhere between the person traveling to edinburgh and the owner of the snake##7
2. the person traveling to paris is not the owner of the rat##6
3. the owner of the mouse is not the person traveling to prague##6
4. the person traveling to prague is somewhere to the right of the owner of the snake##5
5. the person traveling to edinburgh is the owner of the dog##1
6. the person traveling to boston is somewhere to the right of the owner of the dog##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| City   | edinburgh | boston | paris | prague |
| Pet           | dog    | mouse   | snake  | rat      |

