.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-11::.
4 different games are played: backgammon, domino, go, scrabble
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, rock, soul, trance
1. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the fan of gospel##5
2. the fan of soul is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
3. the fan of rock is somewhere to the left of the person playing go##5
4. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
5. the person playing backgammon is between the person playing domino and the fan of rock##2
6. the fan of soul is somewhere between the fan of rock and the person playing domino##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
| Game   | scrabble | backgammon | domino | go   |
| Music-Genre   | rock    | soul      | gospel      | trance |

