2. the person who's hobby is hiking is the cape-cod house##1
3. the craftsman house is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is not the farmhouse house##6
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
6. the farmhouse house is somewhere between the cape-cod house and the person who's hobby is fishing##7
7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the left of the craftsman house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby       | hiking | collecting | filmmaking | fishing |
| House   | cape-cod   | cottage      | farmhouse        | craftsman  |

