4. the fan of house is in an even position##4
5. the person traveling to hamburg is somewhere to the left of the fan of hip-hop##5
6. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the fan of house##1
7. the person traveling to nizza is the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |
| City      | hamburg   | liverpool | nizza | hannover   |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | house   | indie | hip-hop |

