1. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the right of the person watching action movies##5
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is not the person watching documentary movies##6
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the left of the person watching documentary movies##5
5. the person watching horror movies is somewhere between the person watching drama movies and the person who's hobby is drawing##7
6. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
7. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the person watching documentary movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |      3      |    4    |
