.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-19::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, epic, time-travel, zombie
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, july, september, march
1. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##5
4. the person watching zombie movies is on the far left##1
5. the person who's birthday is in march is not the person watching time-travel movies##6
6. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere between the person watching action movies and the person watching time-travel movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |     3     |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | time-travel | epic      | action |
| Birthday     | march  | september  | july | november   |

