.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-20::.
4 different pets are kept: dog, ferret, goldfish, snake
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, german, indian, argentine
1. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere between the indonesian and the owner of the ferret##7
2. the indonesian is on the right of the german##1
3. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
4. the german is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goldfish##5
5. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the indian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Pet         | ferret    | goldfish | snake     | dog |
| Nationality   | indian | argentine  | german | indonesian |

 